      <t>&lt;p&gt;This RFC suggests a simple way for delivering both alphanumeric and numeric pages (one-way) to radio paging terminals.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  This memo does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
